{"tid":1718734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[記者們我地求吓你] 要影警方點部署，唔好影學生點佈防","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:39:30.000Z","uid":79575,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9dd8890f009b30a58fd1c9ec4b00ff581367c03","tid":1718734,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:16:17.000Z","msg":"[記者們我地求吓你] 要影警方點部署，唔好影學生點佈防<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家打緊仗，學生唔夠人，裝備遠遠落後<br />\n<br />\n無論喺中大，理大，浸大，好多記者都係喺學生身後嘅角度直播，有幾多人，有幾多牆，戰線有幾遠等等，<br />\n<ins>學生所有佈防全部俾警察直播睇曬，對警察非常有優勢！</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地跪求記者唔好咁做，學生已經打緊仗，<br />\n知道新聞自由嘅重要性，但係人命都好緊要<br />\n<ins>如果你明嘅，個cam 喺學生角度影警察，或者直接影警察後防，都可以做到新聞</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十萬火急，大戰快要開始，大家一齊推"},{"pid":"aba32afe6689e589f86952bc0a0bd7abe6b9a6eb","tid":1718734,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44adb0da66e059feee5c27b209291034aa54d29c","tid":1718734,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06ae2e3ed177cdec5343d3158d881d3da753ccbe","tid":1718734,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:17:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f51e45aa2ade6f2413b73acf52f2579550f19837","tid":1718734,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"黑記"},{"pid":"aea5b6c7df94917604e928537f7ddabbecad3d15","tid":1718734,"uid":201575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fcd7e3165f45bbce1079dd2fbbeff50db933aa01","tid":1718734,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:18:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17363233b27b17a764c2bd43fb8fa2d256f87e02","tid":1718734,"uid":79575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:23:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bfd45ae2043da5c84b4669828ebc69cac560f044","tid":1718734,"uid":33776